{"tid":1082262,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實散戶做股市預測，大家預測既極限去到邊？","createTime":"2019-03-29T00:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T16:34:07.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba266931e74c721fa43bfd7ef26f7a0096f3ced","tid":1082262,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得做人唔好過份高估自己<br />\n最緊要知道自己個能力做到d 咩<br />\n就例如足球賭博<br />\n我最多做到預測到主隊贏, 客隊輸<br />\n而贏幾多粒波, 幾比幾, 我根本無法預測到<br />\n所以我從來唔會買波膽<br />\n<br />\n想問股票市場<br />\n作為散戶，大家分析預測既極限係去到邊？<br />\n係咪真係摸到最低位知要入貨？要最高位出貨？<br />\n抑或要有明顯轉向，低位升少少先入貨？"},{"pid":"a0956541c15de101658c529165198a62f1b9114e","tid":1082262,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔識"},{"pid":"bfb551f8f913d807e0e270c8a94ccdd5fecb2ffa","tid":1082262,"uid":83654,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"股市根本係Random, 無人可以預測。"},{"pid":"7623951355be9579dedff5fd2b04588f5258dc9f","tid":1082262,"uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bfb551f8f913d807e0e270c8a94ccdd5fecb2ffa","tid":1082262,"uid":83654,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"股市根本係Random, 無人可以預測。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"咁預測唔到仲買黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分析所用既時間都係成本黎<br />\n我省返唔好既"},{"pid":"60c5ac553b45f9fbd418af9300fcb09418db5be1","tid":1082262,"uid":161374,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7623951355be9579dedff5fd2b04588f5258dc9f","tid":1082262,"uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bfb551f8f913d807e0e270c8a94ccdd5fecb2ffa","tid":1082262,"uid":83654,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"股市根本係Random, 無人可以預測。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"咁預測唔到仲買黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />